{"tid":1795072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警曱們，就黎新年啦喎","createTime":"2019-12-23T15:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T07:53:31.000Z","uid":205394,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"01fb516d7608746730ba43882c5aafa38e6c9360","tid":1795072,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"D親戚聚會唔少得架啦<br />\n希望你地今年唔再係被問「幾時結婚」「搵幾多一個月」「幾時生仔」「幾時買樓」呢d問題<br />\n<br />\n希望你地今年聽到既係「幾時去死」「幾時還眼」「幾時被清算」「幾時做condom」啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講新年流流唔好傷和氣，唔好講唔吉利既野<br />\n幾多人因為你地呢一年而受苦呀<br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足應承我，如果你真係有狗做到親戚<br />\n又有機會拜年聚會時見到，一定唔好怯！"},{"pid":"e4bac1182efcad916c43429fa5eb5f21b2fcf050","tid":1795072,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"250c55e139adbabdff8e3f0cdbaeffa18ea5fd15","tid":1795072,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fbf6b67f98dc2dc18edfee0bc637feee8e5cbf","tid":1795072,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:56:30.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"d2dbea0f4c4df8f9d5169e1e71f834fcdae6a192","tid":1795072,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}